title: Australia’s Qube Holdings’ shares jump to record high on Macquarie-led $8.3 billion takeover deal
summary_full: The offer represents a 27.8% premium to Qube's closing price on Nov. 21, the final trading day before the company announced it had entered an exclusivity process.
